  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Texture features are valuable indicators of the surface properties of an image.",
    "Shi et al. (2019) introduced a method based on grayscale co-occurrence matrix (GLCM) using a support vector machine (SVM) classifier to automatically identify underwater cage boundaries.",
    "This technique extracts and computes GLCM features from underwater images by using rich texture information for precise detection of underwater cage boundaries.",
    "Nagaraja et al. (2015) employed robust local binary pattern descriptors to extract texture features from underwater images.",
    "Similarly, Fatan et al. (2016) proposed an underwater cable detection method based on texture information for image edge classification."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Shi et al. (2019) introduced a method based on grayscale co-occurrence matrix (GLCM) using a support vector machine (SVM) classifier to automatically identify underwater cage boundaries.",
    "Nagaraja et al. (2015) employed robust local binary pattern descriptors to extract texture features from underwater images.",
    "Similarly, Fatan et al. (2016) proposed an underwater cable detection method based on texture information for image edge classification."
